---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Primorum"
  description="A Toronto venture studio building the kinds of software businesses that have only recently become possible."
>
  <p class="eyebrow">Primorum</p>

  <h1 class="hero">
    Ventures built for the new software economics.
  </h1>

  <p class="lede">
    AI is making it possible to build kinds of software businesses that were previously
    uneconomical. Primorum is a Toronto venture studio, building them.
  </p>

  <p>
    Each Primorum venture addresses a specific market that has only recently come within reach
    &mdash; niches too small for a traditional team, products too specific for venture capital,
    services that require a quality of attention software is only now able to provide.
  </p>

  <p>
    The defining work is choosing what to build, and building it carefully. Primorum is structured
    around that question.
  </p>
</Base>
